##   depends - awk, curl, echo, espeak-ng, ffmpeg, jq, tr, xmlstarlet, zip
##   conforms-to - <https://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9799919799/utilities/make.html>
##
## See Also:
##
##   * <Project homepage at https://github.com/qq542vev/valvoha>
